Client will invoke the encapsulated object with command and which will execute appropriate receiver

Client (set init setup)  ---> Invoker ---> Command ---> Receiver

Eg.
Client --->      Invoker    ---->       Command ---->      Receiver

Remote AC/TV
Person         Remote  ---->     button   ----->    AC/TV

Stock broker problem

Users       Broker  ----->      Order(Buy/Sell)  ---> Stock